onal_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.5674685092328979, \"rank\": 0.756642067921662, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the final round of 11, Jamaica blanked Kenya 4-0 to regain their crown as the top team in their zone, which was won by Trinidad and Tobago at the last Chess Olympiad held in Chennai, India, in 2022.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9484289773543723, \"rank\": 0.05437519156372667, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.6079981929765115, \"rank\": 0.6445080898970894, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\", \"score\": 0.9999606856324459, \"rank\": 3.931589964960245e-05, \"text\": \"Trinidad\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinidad_and_Tobago\"}, {\"begin\": 738, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chess\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.724203715866173e-17, \"text\": \"Chess\", \"types\": [\"Q1914636\", \"Q11410\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chess\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org